      "comment": "NAVARRE RIVER (5)  kept coming but just failed to pick up the winner as favourite last start over 1400m at Launceston. Had won here prior and can position closer today. Has won over 1600m and is a decent chance to knock over the toppie. BENEFICIARY (1) brings a string of wins from Launceston. Has been backed off the map all three and keeps improving. Has his first start at Hobart and over this longer trip. Feared all the same. GEORGARONI (4) finished on well to just miss behind the above last time and went close here prior. Won his only start here over 1600m and with some weight relief, has to be considered. FIORENTE DE LEGEND (3) settled well back last time, placing distantly over today's journey at this track. Won well prior and her form here at the trip is sound. In the mix.",
